    "description": "你是一名维京勇士，被困在人类世界和瓦尔哈拉之间的一片充满敌意的土地上。凭借自己的智慧和决心，您开始收集幸存者和资源，建立一个新的村庄。在这片崎岖的土地上开辟家园的同时，您还必须保护自己的族人不受堕落战士的伤害。您的旅程将穿越广袤的领土。通过力量和战略，带领你的人民走向辉煌，确保你在瓦尔哈拉的传奇中占有一席之地。<br><br>- 探索与发现<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098850/extras/13442dc49fa2086d25d815114ec5651d.poster.avif?t=1736176363\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098850/extras/13442dc49fa2086d25d815114ec5651d.webm?t=1736176363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098850/extras/13442dc49fa2086d25d815114ec5651d.mp4?t=1736176363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>- 与同伴一起与死神搏斗 <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098850/extras/2d4bb91c8f2a31d4711c131c0baa93ca.poster.avif?t=1736176363\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098850/extras/2d4bb91c8f2a31d4711c131c0baa93ca.webm?t=1736176363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098850/extras/2d4bb91c8f2a31d4711c131c0baa93ca.mp4?t=1736176363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>- 村庄建设： <br>从简陋的起点开始，从头开始建造你的村庄。建造房屋、防御工事、车间等，打造一个能够经受维京时代考验的据点。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098850/extras/e20da0f3ce4aea7db6dd973e47d8deab.poster.avif?t=1736176363\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098850/extras/e20da0f3ce4aea7db6dd973e47d8deab.webm?t=1736176363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098850/extras/e20da0f3ce4aea7db6dd973e47d8deab.mp4?t=1736176363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>- 寻找和招募同伴： <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098850/extras/14d229b1c946126dc6de2e739a78e0b7.poster.avif?t=1736176363\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098850/extras/14d229b1c946126dc6de2e739a78e0b7.webm?t=1736176363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098850/extras/14d229b1c946126dc6de2e739a78e0b7.mp4?t=1736176363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>- 资源管理：<br> 狩猎、采集和开采必要的资源，让你的村庄繁荣昌盛。平衡你对食物、材料和贸易的需求，确保你的人民繁荣昌盛。<br>战斗和征服： 带领你的勇士与敌对阵营和神话生物作战。使用策略和蛮力征服新的领土，扩大您的影响力。<br><br>- 深度手工制作系统：<br>利用环境中收集的原材料制作工具、武器和衣服。尝试不同的组合和品质，打造适合特定任务和战斗场景的装备。",
